ul, hitting Fudou's group with it. Yoh pretends to be possessed and mad just to scare Fudou and unmakes his Over Soul. Mikihisa explains Fudou was possessed by evil spirits before, which is why she grew scared and angry at spirits in general, and she leaves. Mosuke disappears and everybody thinks he returned to paradise, but he is actually trapped in Manta's laptop.
